📋 3. Essential psql Meta-Commands

These commands are used inside the psql shell (they start with \):

Command	Description
\l	List all databases
\c dbname	Connect to a database
\dt	List tables
\d tablename	Describe a table
\du	List users/roles
\dn	List schemas
\df	List functions
\conninfo	Show current connection
\q	Quit
